name: Ballgag
description:
Another model for the kinky people out there, i made this lora model to make it work with well other custom lora models, i've tested it with many of my custom made models and models found here on civitai and it works well, all the images here are done with RealisticVision V20.

The settings i use are: 0.5-0.7 for this lora with 60 steps, Hires.fix (ESRGAN_4 upscaled to 1.5, hires steps 30 with 0.2 denois) W512-H768

These images are not made with custom models and are not real people

A simple "gagged with a ballgag in her mouth" will work fine
